## ===== CANONICAL COMMAND SEQUENCE (Stage 5, successful) =====
# tool: graphify 0.8.39 (PyPI package: graphifyy), installed via: uv tool install graphifyy
# 1) AST code-graph build (NO LLM key required for a code-only corpus):
graphify update target_repo/luigi_buggy --no-cluster
#    -> target_repo/luigi_buggy/graphify-out/graph.json  (6771 nodes, 15365 edges)
# 2) Clustering + report + Obsidian-wiki links (NO LLM via --no-label):
graphify cluster-only target_repo/luigi_buggy --no-label
#    -> GRAPH_REPORT.md (6705 nodes / 13222 edges / 326 communities after dedup)
# 3) Large-graph visual (HTML collapsible tree):
graphify tree --graph target_repo/luigi_buggy/graphify-out/graph.json \
              --output target_repo/luigi_buggy/graphify-out/GRAPH_TREE.html --label luigi_buggy
